---

<Layout>
    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="bg-joomla text-white">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How it works</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white/85">
                Understand the basics of the Joomla REST API and how to start using it in your project.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-12 px-6 py-16">
        <!-- Joomla Version -->
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-joomla">
                ‚úÖ Supported Joomla Versions
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
                Our API is fully compatible with <strong>Joomla 4.x and 5.x</strong>.
                Make sure your Joomla installation is up to date for full feature
                support.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Paid Version Coverage -->
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-joomla">
                üíº What‚Äôs Included in the Paid Version
            </h2>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                <li>Custom route creation</li>
                <li>JWT and OAuth2 authentication support</li>
                <li>Advanced query capabilities</li>
                <li>Email and priority support</li>
                <li>Extended rate limits</li>
                <li>Commercial-use license</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Version Info -->
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-joomla">
                üåê Where to Find the Community Version
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">
                The free and open-source Community Tier is available on our
                <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-joomla underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-joomla/80"
                >GitHub repository</a
                >. It includes essential features and is ideal for testing, learning,
                or personal projects.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-joomla text-white">
        <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col items-center gap-6 px-6 py-16 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Ready to get started?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-white/85">
                Spin up your first endpoint with guided docs, SDKs, and a support team that knows Joomla inside out.
            </p>
            <a
                    href="checkout.html"
                    class="rounded-full bg-white px-10 py-3 font-semibold text-joomla shadow transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg"
            >
                Try It Free
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
